{"word":"ἐγκαταλείπω","slug":"ἐγκαταλείπω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐγκαταλείπω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to leave behind</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to leave in the lurch</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to leave out, omit</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be left behind</i> in a race, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}